{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>Gravenfall: Veil of Darkness</i>, you play as a young hero tasked with lifting a terrible curse that has befallen the village of Gravenfall. The curse emanates from the ominous <strong>Wraithwood Tower</strong>, and its dark magic slowly consumes the land. The village elder, <strong>Maelis</strong>, reveals that a powerful sorcerer within the tower is responsible, and sends you on a dangerous journey to discover how to break it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278390/extras/new_description_image.png?t=1732744438\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Along your quest, you\u2019ll gather resources by <strong>mining</strong>, <strong>cutting down trees</strong>, and <strong>skinning animals</strong> to craft new weapons and armor. <strong>Fishing</strong> provides a way to earn money, and cooked fish can offer valuable health boosts in and out of combat. There are also secrets to uncover, like a <strong>fabled talisman</strong> that can either cure or curse those who possess it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019ll face unique challenges, like <strong>picking locks</strong> to open hidden rooms and buildings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore, battle, and uncover the mysteries of Gravenfall, but beware\u2014dark magic is always watching.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Playtime: 4-8 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732744438","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278390/page.bg.jpg?t=1732744438","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278390/dd9b75d1db049350c61e338ee7a7aadb9a4baf5d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732744438","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as